      "asbval:note": "Paper explicitly validates only Q-Exactive orbitrap and Agilent 6540 Q-TOF. Paper does not provide a complete matrix of all instrument/vendor/acquisition mode combinations, nor does it enumerate Bruker or SCIEX platforms as validated. Paper only states LipidMatch 'can be used with a variety of other vendors' without specifics.",
