    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/card/task_004/scope_drift",
      "@type": "asbval:ScopeDriftAssertion",
      "asbval:drift_notes": [
        "The card frames the task as 'reconstructing' a user-generated library integration module, which implies reverse-engineering or detailed implementation work. The paper describes the capability to use custom libraries but does not detail the internal mechanics of the library loading module itself.",
        "The card's emphasis on 'integration log or status report' as a distinct output is not explicitly supported by the paper, which focuses on final identification results rather than intermediate library-loading diagnostics."
