      "asbval:evidence_quote": "Feature tables should end in 'n.csv' or 'neg.csv' (not case sensitive) for negative mode, and 'p.csv' or 'pos.csv' for positive mode... Each folder should contain respective MS/MS data for that substrate in .ms2 format also ending in 'neg.csv' or 'pos.csv', depending on polarity.",
