      "asbval:evidence_quote": "For each MS/MS scan of each feature, experimental fragments are matched against in silico lipid fragments m/z using a tolerance window (ppm)... Lipids are identified if they contain the necessary observed fragments... If multiple lipids are identified for a single feature, the lipids are ranked by the summed intensity of all their fragments with in silico fragment exact mass matches",
