      "asbval:evidence_quote": "LipidMatch currently has over 250,000 lipid species spanning 56 lipid types contained in in silico fragmentation libraries... LipidMatch uses rule-based identification... For each lipid candidate, the intensities of experimental fragments with exact mass matches to expected in silico fragments are summed.",
